item.description:
Hey Incubators!

A long time ago in a galaxy far far away...

We had an awesome incubator named Renee who moved away =o( Alas she now returns on a one day tour to the improv incubator!

For those that know Renee, come rejoice! For those that don't, come meet the legend...

and come along for the usual smorgesbord of improv games and laughter that occur on a weekly basis!

Remember no expereience required! A big shout out to all those who have not come before, come on down, you're the next constestant!

Any questions? Let me know!

Just come on around to the backyard once you get to the address below!

Cheers

Jason
item.name: Improv Incubator: Episode VI Return of the Renee
